Rock Paper Scissors Game
 A simple command-line Rock Paper Scissors game built with Python, where you play against the computer. Keep track of wins, losses, and ties with a running score.

Features
 Play Rock, Paper, Scissors against the computer.
 Real-time score tracking for you, the computer, and ties.
 Simple and interactive command-line interface.
 Option to replay multiple rounds until you decide to quit.
Notes
 The game is case-insensitive; Rock, rock, or ROCK all work.
 Invalid inputs will prompt a warning without affecting scores.
